<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SOC-SIDEKICKS-KNIGHTS-TEX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
SIDEKICKS RECOVER, TATTOO KNIGHTS, 10-2
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TROY PHILLIPS 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   DALLAS _ It's a familiar, peculiar habit the Dallas Sidekicks
have developed the past few seasons.
