in the 1996 presidential election, a new Census Bureau report
shows. One exception: Naturalized Hispanic voters who show ardor in
the political process. (Shepard, Cox Washington Bureau)
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON _ Setup for Clinton's videotaped testimony for Starr.
