NYT-08-16-98 1802EDT &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19980816.0091 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-16 18:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6162 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TV-WRESTLING-MEDIA-AR     08-16 1034
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TV-WRESTLING-MEDIA-ART-2TAKES-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
CABLE AND NETWORKS CLINCH OVER WRESTLING AD REVENUE 
</HEADLINE>
  (Duplication warning: Also moved in `f' category) 
(ART ADV: A graphic is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling (888)
603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
(mk) 
 By BILL CARTER   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
