<HEADLINE>
MIDDLE-AGED MIG PILOTS HAVING FAUX DOGFIGHTS OVER THE HEARTLAND 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Wis., Mo., Ill., Ala., Vt.)  (Duplication warning: Also moving in ``a'' category) 
