<HEADER>
A6341 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-HEALTHCARE-     08-16 0037
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-HEALTHCARE-BANKRUPTCY-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   HEALTHCARE-BANKRUPTCY (Philadelphia) will not move in tonight's
New York Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, August 16.
</P>
</TEXT>
